%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E's%20separation%20from%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%20was%20one%20of%20the%20major%20talking%20points%20about%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025%20retention%20phase%20ahead%20of%20the%20mega%20auction.%20Rahul%20and%20LSG%20parted%20ways%20after%20three%20years%2C%20with%20the%20batter%20revealing%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20go%20back%20into%20the%20auction%20pool.%20Following%20the%20retention%20announcement%2C%20LSG%20owner%20Sanjiv%20Goenka%20had%20stated%20that%20the%20franchise%20retained%20players%20who%20they%20believed%20would%20put%20the%20team%20ahead%20of%20personal%20ambition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20simple%20mindset%20to%20go%20in%20for%20players%2C%20who%20have%20a%20mindset%20to%20win%2C%20who%20put%20the%20team%20before%20their%20personal%20goals%20and%20personal%20aspirations%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanjiv%20Goenka%20said%20after%20LSG%20announced%20its%20set%20of%20retained%20players%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202025%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Rahul%20responded%20to%20these%20statements.%20When%20asked%20whether%20Goenka's%20statements%20had%20played%20a%20part%20in%20triggering%20Rahul's%20decision%20to%20part%20ways%2C%20the%20batter%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20had%20been%20made%20beforehand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20was%20made%20already.%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20the%20comments%20are%20but%20they%20must%20have%20come%20after%20the%20retentions%20were%20made.%20Just%20felt%20like%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20fresh%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20explore%20my%20options%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20play%20somewhere%20I%20can%20find%20some%20freedom%20and%20team%20atmosphere%20would%20be%20something%20lighter%2C%20much%20more%20balanced%2C%20pressure%20is%20already%20very%20high%20in%20the%20IPL%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rahul%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9vH0cytrd4o%26t%3D1s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStar%20Sports%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20had%20been%20LSG's%20captain%20in%20its%20first%20three%20years%20in%20the%20IPL.%20He%20amassed%20616%20runs%20in%202022%2C%20but%20that%20tally%20fell%20dramatically%20in%20an%20injury-driven%202023%20campaign.%20In%20his%20three%20years%20at%20the%20franchise%2C%20Rahul's%20defensive%20approach%20came%20under%20intense%20scrutiny%2C%20with%20his%20strike%20rate%20being%20below%20135%20during%20the%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20Rahul%20mentioned%20the%20need%20to%20maintain%20a%20balanced%20culture%20and%20team%20atmosphere%20within%20a%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20play%20in%20a%20team%20atmosphere%20where%20it%20is%20lighter.%20Dressing%20rooms%20like%20GT%20(Gujarat%20Titans)%20and%20CSK%20(Chennai%20Super%20Kings)%20seem%20balanced%20and%20calm%20even%20when%20they%20lose%2C%20and%20that%20is%20important%20to%20me%20as%20a%20player%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tried%20that%20at%20LSG%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Andy%20Flower%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F189-andy-flower-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAndy%20Flower%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20GG%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E)%20at%20first%2C%20and%20then%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Justin%20Langer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F267-justin-langer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJustin%20Langer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it%20was%20brilliant.%20But%20sometimes%20you%20have%20to%20move%20away%20and%20find%20something%20for%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20will%