ement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-aishwarya-rai-opened-up-about-being-hypersensitive-to-public-scrutiny-i-wish-i-was-more-tough%2Farticleshow%2F115228601.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCombining%20Indian%20Hospitality%20With%20Swiss%20Quality%26quot%3B%3A%20CEO%20On%20New%20Noida%20Airport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Capital%20Region%20is%20set%20to%20get%20its%20second%20major%20airport%20in%20April%20next%20year%20and%20with%20the%20first%20trial%20flights%20scheduled%20a%20few%20days%20from%20now%20at%20the%20Noida%20International%20Airport%20-%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Jewar%20airport%20-%20NDTV%20has%20got%20an%20exclusive%20behind-the-scenes%20look%20at%20the%20frenetic%20construction%20activity%20at%20the%20project%20site%20as%20well%20as%20details%20of%20its%20design%2C%20connectivity%20and%20projected%20passenger%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20also%20spoke%20exclusively%20to%20Noida%20International%20Airport%20CEO%20Christoph%20Schnellmann%2C%20who%20said%20their%20aim%20is%20to%20provide%20a%20passenger%20experience%20that%20combines%20Indian%20warmth%20and%20hospitality%20with%20Swiss%20quality%20and%20efficiency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20is%20being%20developed%20by%20the%20Yamuna%20International%20Airport%20Private%20Limited%2C%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Swiss%20firm%20Zurich%20Airport%20International%20AG%2C%20in%20association%20with%20the%20Noida%20International%20Airport%20Limited%2C%20which%20is%20the%20implementing%20agency%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20Jewar%20in%20Western%20UP's%20Gautam%20Buddha%20Nagar%20district%2C%20the%20airport%20is%20scheduled%20to%20see%20its%20first%20trial%20flights%20taking%20off%20and%20touching%20down%20in%20a%20few%20days%2C%20which%20will%20be%20an%20important%20milestone%20not%20only%20in%20the%20airport's%20development%20schedule%20but%20also%20in%20the%20story%20of%20the%20growth%20of%20Indian%20aviation.%20The%20airport%20was%20necessary%20given%20that%20the%20Indian%20aviation%20market%20has%20seen%20a%20compounded%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%208.9%25%20in%20the%20decade%20between%202013%20and%202023%20and%20because%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20in%20Delhi%20has%20reached%20its%20growth%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%20Influences%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Schnellmann%20said%20design%20has%20been%20a%20key%20focus%20for%20the%20company%20since%20the%20project%20began%20around%20five%20years%20ago.%20Local%20materials%20have%20been%20used%20and%20one%20of%20the%20standout%20design%20choices%20is%20the%20flight%20of%20steps%20at%20the%20terminal's%20forecourt%2C%20which%20will%20resemble%20the%20ghats%20of%20Varanasi%20and%20Haridwar.%20Reflecting%20a%20focus%20on%20a%20climate%20change-friendly%20approach%2C%20the%20airport%20will%20also%20use%20natural%20lighting%20and%20ventilation%20to%20reduce%20its%20environmental%20footprint%20and%20energy%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20incredibly%20excited%20about%20the%20experience%20we%20are%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20offer%20our%20passengers.%20We%20talk%20about%20combining%20Indian%20warmth%20and%20hospitality%20with%20Swiss%20quality%20and%20efficiency.%20I%20think%20we%20have%20been%20very%20deliberate%20about%20designing%20the%20terminal%20(by)%20picking%20up%20elements%20of%20the%20rich%20architectural%20heritage%20of%20the%20region...%20An%20airport%20that%20is%20very%20much%20at%20home%20in%20north%20India%2C%20in%20Western%20UP.%20The%20commercial%20space%20will%20feature%20a%20large%20open-air%20courtyard%20reminiscent%20of%20some%20of%20the%20'%3Cem%3Ehavelis'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(traditional%20houses)%20found%20in%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20has%20also%20been%20planned%20as%20a%20gateway%20to%20tourist%20destinations%20in%20North%20India%2C%20including%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%2C%20and%20for%20Hindu%20pilgrimages%20like%20the%20Chardham%20Yatra%2C%20Kumbh%20Mela%2C%20Mathura%20and%20Vrindavan%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Buddhist%20circuit%20of%20Sravasti%2C%20Kapilavastu%20and%20Kushinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber-Crunching%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20area%20of%20the%20project%20is%201%2C334%20hectares%20and%2C%20in%20its%20first%20phase%2C%201.2%20crore%20passengers%20are%20expected%20to%20use%20the%20airport%20every%20year.%20The%20number%20is%20projected%20to%20increase%20to%203%20crore%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade%20and%207%20crore%20a%20few%20years%20after%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20runway%20will%20be%20operational%20initially%20and%2C%20when%20it%20opens%2C%20the%20terminal%20will%20have%2010%20aerobridges%20and%20three%20bus%20gates.%20There%20will%20eventually%20be%20two%20operational%20runways%20and%20while%20the%20airport%20will%20have%2028%20spots%20for%20aircraft%20in%20the%20apron%20area%20initially%2C%20this%20will%20expand%20to%20200%20as%20the%20flights%20and%20passenger%20count%20increase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Schnellmann%20said%20that%20the%20terminal%20is%20being%20built%20keeping%20this%20expansion%20in%20mind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pier%20can%20expand%20to%20the%20west%20to%20provide%20further%20passenger%20capacity.%20The%20building%20has%20also%20been%20designed%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20it%20can%20be%20mirrored%20to%20the%20east%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoad%2C%20Rail%20Links%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20is%20connected%20to%20Greater%20Noida%2C%20Noida%20and%20Delhi%20via%20the%20signal-free%20Yamuna%20Expressway.%20Leaving%20from%20Saket%20at%2011%20am%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20it%20took%20about%20an%20hour%20and%2045%20minutes%20to%20reach%20the%20airport%20by%20road.%20Once%20an%20interchange%20is%20built%20from%20the%20airport%20to%20the%20expressway%2C%20it%20will%20take%20approximately%2045%20minutes%20from%20Noida%20and%2025%20minutes%20from%20Greater%20Noida%2C%20according%20to%20Mr%20Schnellmann.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20said%20the%20UP%20government%20is%20also%20planning%20a%20rail%20link%20directly%20to%20the%20airport%2C%20construction%20on%20which%20will%20begin%20in%20a%20year%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731435660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fj4kik598_noida-airport_625x300_12_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjewar-airport-noida-airport-second-delhi-airport-up-combining-indian-hospitality-with-swiss-quality-ceo-on-new-noida-airport-7004921%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Capital%20Region%20is%20set%20to%20get%20its%20second%20major%20airport%20in%20April%20next%20year%20and%20with%20the%20first%20trial%20flights%20scheduled%20a%20few%20days%20from%20now%20at%20the%20Noida%20International%20Airport%2C%20NDTV%20has%20got%20an%20exclusive%20behind-the-scenes%20look.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjewar-airport-noida-airport-second-delhi-airport-up-combining-indian-hospitality-with-swiss-quality-ceo-on-new-noida-airport-7004921%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20Bans%20%26quot%3BWestern%20Liberal%20Propaganda%26quot%3B%20Of%20Choosing%20Not%20To%20Have%20Children%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERussian%20MPs%20on%20Tuesday%20passed%20in%20the%20final%20third%20reading%20controversial%20legislation%20banning%20%26quot%3Bpropaganda%26quot%3B%20of%20choosing%20not%20to%20have%20children%2C%20the%20latest%20measure%20targeting%20what%20Moscow%20depicts%20as%20Western%20liberal%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFacing%20an%20ageing%20population%20and%20low%20birth%20rates%2C%20Moscow%20is%20seeking%20to%20reverse%20a%20demographic%20slump%20-%20accentuated%20by%20its%20military%20offensive%20on%20Ukraine%20-%20that%20threatens%20its%20economic%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMPs%20in%20the%20Duma%20lower%20house%20of%20parliament%20voted%20unanimously%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20draft%20bill%2C%20which%20would%20apply%20to%20materials%20online%2C%20in%20media%2C%20advertising%20and%20in%20films%20that%20promote%20%26quot%3Brejection%20of%20childbearing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20targets%20%26quot%3Bdestructive%20content%26quot%3B%20that%20promotes%20a%20%26quot%3Bconscious%26quot%3B%20rejection%20of%20having%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill's%20authors%20have%20said%20it%20will%20not%20be%20used%20as%20punishment%20for%20%26quot%3Ba%20personal%20choice%20or%20lifestyle%26quot%3B%20but%20only%20for%20promoting%20such%20a%20lifestyle%2C%20although%20it%20is%20unclear%20how%20this%20would%20be%20differentiated%20in%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolations%20would%20be%20punishable%20by%20fines%20up%20to%20400%2C000%20rubles%20(%244%2C000)%20on%20individuals%20and%20up%20to%20five%20million%20rubles%20for%20businesses.%20The%20bill%20also%20includes%20a%20provision%20to%20deport%20foreigners%20found%20guilty%20of%20disseminating%20the%20banned%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20fateful%20law...%20Without%20children%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20country.%20This%20ideology%20will%20lead%20to%20people%20stopping%20giving%20birth%20to%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Duma's%20speaker%20Vyacheslav%20Volodin%20said%20ahead%20of%20the%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20legislation%20was%20about%20%26quot%3Bprotecting%20citizens%2C%20primarily%20the%20generation%20growing%20up%2C%20from%20information%20spread%20in%20the%20media%20space%20that%20negatively%20affects%20the%20development%20of%20personality%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20%26quot%3Bso%20new%20generations%20of%20our%20citizens%20grow%20up%20orientated%20towards%20traditional%20family%20values%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENina%20Ostanina%2C%20a%20Communist%20Party%20MP%20who%20heads%20the%20Duma%20committee%20on%20family%20policy%2C%20said%20the%20bill%20aims%20to%20%26quot%3Bguard%20our%20youth%20from%20unnecessary%20ideologies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20will%20now%20be%20considered%20by%20the%20upper%20house%20of%20parliament%20on%20November%2020%2C%20before%20coming%20before%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20who%20is%20expected%20to%20sign%20it%20into%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20on%20top%20of%20existing%20bans%20on%20%26quot%3Bpropaganda%26quot%3B%20of%20LGBTQ%20relationships%20or%20changing%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EADOPTION%20BAN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Duma%20also%20unanimously%20passed%20legislation%20in%20the%20third%20reading%20banning%20foreigners%20living%20in%20countries%20that%20allow%20gender%20reassignment%20from%20adopting%20Russian%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20is%20aimed%20at%20stopping%20Russian%20children%20from%20being%20able%20to%20legally%20change%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoscow%20has%20long%20portrayed%20itself%20as%20a%20bulwark%20against%20liberal%20values%2C%20but%20that%20trend%20has%20hugely%20accelerated%20since%20the%20Kremlin%20launched%20its%20Ukraine%20offensive%2C%20further%20rupturing%20ties%20with%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20would%20ban%20adoption%20by%20citizens%20of%20countries%20that%20authorise%20%26quot%3Bthe%20change%20of%20sex%20by%20medical%20intervention%2C%20including%20with%20the%20use%20of%20medicine%26quot%3B%2C%20or%20allow%20individuals%20to%20change%20their%20gender%20on%20official%20identity%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%201993%2C%20foreigners%20have%20adopted%20102%2C403%20children%20from%20Russia%2C%20Volodin%20said%2C%20warni