n%20the%20air%20show%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Russias%20Su-57%20participated%20in%20the%20air%20show%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F9211cga_su57_625x300_12_November_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20Su-57%20participated%20in%20the%20air%20show%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20AFP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airshow%20will%20feature%20a%20dedicated%20drone%20zone%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20The%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20has%20shown%20the%20world%20the%20growing%20relevance%20of%20drones%20on%20the%20battlefield%20and%20how%20it%20is%20being%20used%20extensively%20by%20Kyiv%20to%20counter%20the%20asymmetry%20in%20terms%20of%20military%20strength%20with%20Russia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20unveiled%20its%20'%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fmilitary%2Farticle%2F3285955%2Fchina-unveils-killer-whale-stealth-drone-ship%5C%22%3EKiller%20Whale%3C%2Fa%3E'%20ship%20ahead%20of%20the%20largest%20air%20show.%20The%20dual%20diesel%20and%20electric%20propulsion%20ship%20is%20unmanned%20and%20can%20carry%20a%20range%20of%20weapons%20like%20rockets%2C%20anti-ship%20missiles%20and%20ship-to-air%20missiles.%20It%20can%20also%20allow%20take-off%20and%20landing%20of%20choppers%20at%20its%20helipad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20Killer%20Whale%20is%20not%20the%20first%20unmanned%20surface%20vessel%20developed%20by%20a%20country.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20US%20Navy%20completed%20its%20first%20deployment%20of%20four%20unmanned%20ships%20which%20spent%20over%20four%20months%20in%20the%20Pacific%20for%20sea%20trials.%20The%20unmanned%20surface%20vessels%20-%20Sea%20Hunter%2C%20Sea%20Hawk%2C%20Mariner%20and%20Ranger%20-%20departed%20Southern%20California%20in%20August%202023%20and%20returned%20in%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20AMCA%20Program%