0Letter%20To%20ICC%20On%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20Target%20Is%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20has%20written%20to%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20seeking%20reasons%20behind%20India's%20refusal%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20play%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20next%20year%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fstory%2Fchampions-trophy-2025-pcb-wants-an-explanation-in-writing-from-india-for-refusal-to-travel-1459337%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EESPN%20Cricinfo%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday.%20Last%20week%2C%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20informed%20the%20PCB%20that%20the%20BCCI%2C%20after%20not%20receiving%20permission%20form%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20has%20not%20agreed%20to%20send%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%202025%20Champions%20Trophy.%20The%20report%20added%20the%20PCB%20wants%20in%20writing%20from%20BCCI%2C%20detailing%20the%20reasons%20and%20justification.%20behind%20it%20not%20being%20able%20to%20attend%20the%20event%20in%20Pakistan%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20played%20across%20three%20venues%20in%20Pakistan%20from%20February%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20tense%20political%20ties%20between%20both%20nations%2C%20India%20has%20not%20travelled%20to%20Pakistan%20since%202008%2C%20when%20they%20played%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20over%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20firmly%20held%20the%20stance%20of%20not%20travelling%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20citing%20'security%20concerns'.%3Cbr%3E%5CnEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20BCCI%20vice-president%20Rajeev%20Shukla%20stated%20that%20India%20would%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20only%20if%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20permitted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20ICC%20conveyed%20to%20the%20PCB%20in%20writing%20that%20India%20won't%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20marquee%20event%20which%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20early%20months%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PCB%20consulted%20with%20the%20Pakistan%20government%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20is%20looking%20to%20present%20a%20firm%20stance%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20India's%20participation%20contributes%20to%20ICC's%20revenue%2C%20the%20PCB's%20role%20is%20equally%20crucial%2C%20and%20without%20Pakistan-India%20matches%2C%20the%20ICC%20revenues%20would%20suffer%20significantly%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20told%20Geo%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20has%20requested%20the%20ICC%20to%20conduct%20the%20match%20of%20the%20Indian%20Cricket%20Team%20on%20a%20hybrid%20model%20with%20the%20final%20to%20likely%20take%20place%20at%20Dubai%20International%20Stadium%20in%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20last%20week%2C%20PCB%20chairman%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20shrugged%20away%20the%20possibility%20of%20hosting%20the%20tournament%20in%20a%20hybrid%20model%20by%20claiming%20that%20there%20have%20been%20no%20discussions%20about%20hosting%20the%20tournament%20in%20a%20hybrid%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20sources%20reported%20that%20South%20Africa%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20emerged%20as%20possible%20venues%20for%20hosting%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%202025%20if%20Pakistan%20pulled%20out%20at%20the%20last%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20tournament%20is%20shifted%2C%20there%20are%20also%20chances%20that%20Pakistan%20could%20withdraw%20from%20the%20tournament%20if%20ICC%20moves%20the%20tournament%20to%20a%20neutral%20venue%2C%20according%20to%20recent%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%20played%20their%20last%20bilateral%20series%20in%202012-13%20in%20India%2C%20a%20white-ball%20series%20and%20now%20mostly%20play%20in%20ICC%20tournaments%20and%20Asia%20Cups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731427920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F3njrvrcg_mohsin-naqvi-_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-cricket-board-shoots-off-tough-letter-to-icc-on-champions-trophy-target-is-india-7004244%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20of%20now%2C%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20played%20across%20three%20venues%20in%20Pakistan%20from%20February%209.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-cricket-board-shoots-off-tough-letter-to-icc-on-champions-trophy-target-is-india-7004244%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Imported%20Seeds%2C%20Full-Spectrum%20Lights%3A%20High-Tech%20Marijuana%20Op%20Busted%20In%20Noida%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20high-tech%20marijuana%20operation%2C%20using%20imported%20seeds%20and%20full-spectrum%20grow%20lights%2C%20has%20been%20busted%20in%20Greater%20Noida%20and%20an%20English%20graduate%20from%20Meerut%20has%20been%20arrested.%20Police%20said%20the%20man%20cultivated%20at%20least%20100%20marijuana%20plants%2C%20including%20premium%20(OG)%20and%20other%20varieties%2C%20at%20his%20flat%20in%20Beta-2's%20Parsvnath%20Panorama%20society%2C%20selling%20the%20produce%20from%20each%20of%20them%20on%20the%20dark%20web%20for%20between%20Rs%2050%2C000%20and%20Rs%2060%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20inspired%20to%20get%20into%20the%20drug%20trade%20after%20watching%20web%20series%20and%20used%20to%20gather%20information%20on%20growing%20marijuana%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20said%20an%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBriefing%20reporters%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20said%20the%20accused%2C%20Rahul%20Chowdhary%2C%20would%20grow%20premium%20marijuana%20(OG)%20in%20flower%20pots%20by%20pur