%20a%20protest%20against%20acquisition%20of%20land%20for%20a%20pharmaceutical%20project.%20The%20protest%20took%20place%20in%20Lagacharla%20village%20of%20Dudyala%20mandal%2C%20which%20falls%20under%20Kodangal%20assembly%20seat%20represented%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20A%20Revanth%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20officials%20-%20Kodangal%20Area%20Development%20Authority%20(KADA)%20chairman%20Venkat%20Reddy%2C%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Srinivas%20Reddy%2C%20Additional%20Collector%20Lingya%20Naik%20and%20Mandal%20Revenue%20Officer%20Vijay%20Kumar%20-%20sustained%20injuries%20after%20villagers%20attacked%20the%20officials%20with%20sticks%20and%20threw%20stones%20at%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspector%20General%20of%20Police%20(Multi%20Zone%20II)%20V.%20Satyanarayana%20told%20news%20agency%20IANS%20that%20the%20attack%20on%20officials%20was%20%26quot%3Bpre-planned%26quot%3B%20allegedly%20by%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20youth%20wing%20leader%20B%20Suresh%20Raj%2C%20who%20is%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatyanarayana%20also%20said%20that%20police%20believe%20100-110%20people%20participated%20in%20the%20attack.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20take%20stringent%20action%20against%20those%20who%20took%20part%20in%20the%20attack%20and%20those%20who%20instigated%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20when%20a%20team%20of%20officials%2C%20led%20by%20Collector%20Prateek%20Jain%2C%20visited%20the%20village%20to%20seek%20the%20locals'%20opinion%20on%20the%20proposed%20land%20acquisition%20for%20the%20pharma%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20aware%20of%20the%20details%20said%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20acquire%201%2C358%20acres%20of%20land%20for%20the%20pharma%20project.%20Farmers%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20the%20compensation%20offered%20is%20lower%20than%20market%20rates%2C%20and%20have%20expressed%20their%20apprehensions%20about%20losing%20their%20land%20and%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20Collector's%20office%20had%20set%20up%20a%20camp%20on%20Monday%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Lagacharla%20to%20seek%20public%20opinion%20when%20Raj%20approached%20the%20officials%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20visit%20the%20village%20instead%20for%20the%20discussion.%20As%20the%20collector%20and%20his%20team%20reached%20the%20spot%2C%20the%20villagers%20attacked%20them%20and%20raised%20slogans%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bcollector%20go%20back%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRaj%20had%20people%20ready%20to%20attack%20the%20officers%20who%20showed%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Satyanarayana%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20staffers%20at%20the%20Collector's%20office%20staged%20a%20dharna%20against%20the%20attack%2C%20even%20as%20the%20official%20said%20he%20was%20not%20attacked%20by%20the%20villagers.%20Other%20government%20employees%20in%20the%20district%20boycotted%20their%20duties%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20employees%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20state%20wore%20black%20badges%2C%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Telangana%20minister%20Sridhar%20Babu%20said%20the%20state%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20serious%20view%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20which%20was%20planned%20by%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20elements%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20stop%20development%20in%20Telangana%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20dismissed%20BRS%20working%20president%20K%20T%20Rama%20Rao's%20allegation%20that%20the%20pharma%20project%20would%20benefit%20a%20relative%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731425160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fdvt529ng_telangana-vikarabad-violence_625x300_12_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelangana-vikarabad-clash-land-acquisition-revanth-reddy-7003744%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2055%20people%20in%20Telangana's%20Vikarabad%20district%20were%20detained%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20allegedly%20attacking%20government%20officials%20during%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20acquisition%20of%20land%20for%20a%20pharmaceutical%20project.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelangana-vikarabad-clash-land-acquisition-revanth-reddy-7003744%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20ex-congressman%20paralysed%20after%20polo%20accident%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731424818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Ff686%2Flive%2F77a19760-a102-11ef-8f5b-3de8566d4c06.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc39n79l4ppwo%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20friend%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Republican%20said%20September's%20accident%20left%20him%20paralysed%20from%20the%20chest%20down.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A240%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc39n79l4ppwo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc39n79l4ppwo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc39n79l4ppwo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt's...%26quot%3B%3A%20Chess%20World%20No.%201%20Carlsen%20Reveals%20Why%20He%20Does%20Not%20Play%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMagnus%20Carlsen%2C%20the%20undisputed%20world%20number%20one%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20believes%20chess%20ratings%20today%20are%20somewhat%20%26quot%3Bdeflated%26quot%3B%20compared%20to%20the%20past%20but%20remains%20unfazed%20by%20the%20possibility%20of%20someone%20surpassing%20him.%20The%20five-time%20world%20champion%2C%20who%20held%20the%20title%20from%202013%20to%202023%2C%20chose%20not%20to%20defend%20his%20crown%2C%20citing%20lack%20of%20motivation.%20Despite%20stepping%20back%20from%20classical%20tournaments%2C%20Carlsen's%20reign%20at%20the%20top%20is%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20and%20most%20dominant%20in%20chess%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20play%20a%20lot%20of%20classical%20chess%2C%20so%20whenever%20somebody%20is%20going%20to%20pass%20me%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20particularly%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2033-year-old%20Norwegian%20said%20during%20a%20media%20interaction%20ahead%20of%20the%20Tata%20Steel%20Chess%20India%20Rapid%20and%20Blitz%20tournament%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20surpass%20me%2C%20but%20we'll%20see%20when%20it%20happens.%20I%20think%20it%20sort%20of%20depends%20on%20others.%26quot%3B%20Carlsen%20also%20suggested%20that%20chess%20ratings%20may%20not%20carry%20the%20same%20weight%20they%20did%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20definitely%20been%20deflation%20in%20chess%20ratings%2C%20so%20a%20level%20of%20ELO%202830%20would%20probably%20correspond%20to%202850%20about%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20reached%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20noted%20Carlsen%2C%20who%20currently%20has%20a%20FIDE%20rating%20of%202831.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20held%20the%20world%20number%201%20spot%20almost%20continuously%20since%20July%201%2C%202011%2C%20Carlsen%20first%20achieved%20the%20top%20ranking%20in%20January%202010%20at%20the%20age%20of%2019%2C%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20player%20to%20reach%20that%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20briefly%20losing%20it%20in%20mid%202011%2C%20he%20reclaimed%20the%20top%20spot%20and%20has%20dominated%20it%20ever%20since.%20Throughout%20his%20career%2C%20Carlsen%20has%20set%20multiple%20records%2C%20including%20the%20highest%20FIDE%20rating%20ever%20recorded%20at%202882%20in%20May%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20opting%20out%20of%20the%20World%20Championship%20in%202023%2C%20Carlsen%20has%20%26quot%3Bpicked%20and%20chosen%26quot%3B%20tournaments%20with%20formats%20and%20opponents%20he%20finds%20exciting%2C%20focusing%20on%20rapid%2C%20blitz%2C%20and%20other%20flexible%20events%20that%20align%20with%20his%20evolving%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20younger%20generation%20of%20players%2C%20Carlsen%20conveyed%20his%20respect%20for%20their%20progress%20while%20noting%20that%20they%20don't%20always%20measure%20up%20to%20his%20level%2C%20a%20statement%20more%20reflective%20of%20his%20confidence%20than%20arrogance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20looking%20forward%20to%20testing%20myself%20against%20the%20younger%20generation.%20I'm%20always%20curious%20to%20see%20how%20much%20they've%20improved%20since%20the%20last%20time.%20It%20turns%20out%20they%20have%20improved%2C%20but%20not%20always%20enough.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20look%20forward%20to%20seeing%20all%20the%20Indian%20chess%20fans.%20It's%20quite%20chaotic%3B%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20I%20don't%20do%20play%20here%20every%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Carlsen%20who%20is%20here%20to%20play%20the%20tournament%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarlsen%20has%20won%20the%20World%20Rapid%20Chess%20Championship%20four%20times%20(2014%2C%202015%2C%202019%2C%20and%202022)%20and%20the%20World%20Blitz%20Chess%20Championship%20five%20times%20(2009%2C%202014%2C%202017%2C%202018%2C%20and%202019)%2C%20making%20him%20one%20of%20the%20most%20versatile%20and%20dominant%20world%20champions%20across%20different%20formats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20younger%20generation%20of%20chess%20players%2C%20Carlsen%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20interesting%20to%20see%20a%20different%20brand%20of%20chess.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20older%20players%20of%20my%20generation%20are%20not%20going%20to%20surprise%20you%20in%20a%20major%20way%20in%20terms%20of%20where%20they%20stand%2C%20but%20with%20the%20younger%20generation%2C%20it's%20interesting%20to%20try%20and%20understand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarlsen%20began%20his%20reign%20after%20defeating%20Viswanathan%20Anand%20in%20the%20World%20Championship%20in%20Chennai%20in%202013%20and%20he%20feels%20the%20country%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20to%20Chennai%20in%20August%20(2013)%2C%20to%20look%20at%20the%20facilities%20and%20so%20on.%20I%20was%20told%20that%20I'm%20going%20to%20meet%20some%20of%20the%20better%20kids%20in%20the%20area%20to%20play%2C%20and%20it%20feels%20like%20half%20of%20the%20kids%20are%20now%20either%20GMs%20or%20some%20of%20them%20are%20even%20playing%20in%20top%20tournaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20has%20changed.%20Those%20kids%20back%20then%20are%20now%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Olympiad-winning%20team.%20Indian%20chess%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20since%20then%2C%20much%20thanks%20to%20Anand%20and%20what%20he%20did%20for%20Indian%20chess%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarlsen%20was%20also%20impressed%20with%20three-year-old%20chess%20prodigy%20from%20the%20city%20Anish%20Sarkar%2C%20who%20recently%20became%20the%20youngest%20FIDE-rated%20chess%20player%20in%20the%20world%20with%20a%20rating%20of%201555.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20it's%20amazing%20to%20see%20the%20level%20he's%20at.%20My%20nephew%20is%20turning%204%2C%20he's%20a%20bright%20young%20child%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20see%20him%20getting%20a%20rating%20of%201500%20anytime%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20impressive.%20Most%20of%20all%2C%20try%20to%20enjoy%20as%20much%20as%20you%20can.%20Don't%20think%20about%20ratings%2C%20results%2C%20titles%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20They%20will%20come%20automatically%3B%20just%20do%20what%20you%20love%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20signed%20off%2C%20while%20posing%20for%20a%20photo%20with%20the%20kid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20th