20ball%20the%20opposite%20ways.%20But%20Lyon%20has%20been%20someone%20who%20has%20bowled%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20over-spin.%20That%20challenges%20the%20batters%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Adams%2C%2047%2C%20in%20a%20virtual%20interaction%20arranged%20by%20SA20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20India's%20key%20pacer%20Mohammed%20Shami%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Australia-bound%20squad%20for%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20series%2C%20Adams%20felt%20the%20stalwarts%20services%20will%20be%20dearly%20missed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20he%20(Shami)%20will%20be%20a%20major%20miss%20for%20India%2C%20given%20the%20Australian%20conditions.%20The%20pace%20and%20bouncy%20wickets%20in%20Australia%20would%20have%20helped%20India%20in%20gaining%20an%20upper%20hand%20if%20Shami%20had%20been%20in%20the%20squad%20but%20that's%20not%20in%20the%20selector's%20hand%20as%20he%20is%20recovering%2C%20but%20I%20think%20he%20will%20be%20missed%2C%26quot%3B%20Adams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%2C%20who%20has%20been%20out%20of%20action%20since%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%20final%20on%20November%2019%20due%20to%20an%20ankle%20injury%20and%20subsequent%20surgery%2C%20will%20aim%20to%20prove%20his%20fitness%20in%20a%20real-match%20situation%20after%20undergoing%20intense%20rehabilitation%20at%20the%20BCCI%20Centre%20of%20Excellence%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20make%20his%20much-anticipated%20return%20to%20competitive%20cricket%20after%20a%20hiatus%20of%20nearly%20a%20year%20through%20Bengal's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20match%20against%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%20Indore%20from%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Cricket%20Association%20of%20Bengal%20has%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdams%20added%20that%20Shami's%20absence%20will%20put%20more%20pressure%20on%20pace%20spearhead%20Jasprit%20Bumrah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20saw%20what%20he%20(Shami)%20did%20in%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%20He%20single-handedly%20carried%20the%20Indian%20pace%20attack%20and%20he%20is%20som