0Himalayas%2C%20Sangti%20village%2C%20a%20pristine%20paradise%2C%20is%20home%20to%20the%20Monpa%20people%20%E2%80%94%20a%20vibrant%20community%20steeped%20in%20tradition.%20Yet%2C%20even%20in%20this%20idyllic%20setting%2C%20the%20spectre%20of%20pollution%20has%20cast%20a%20long%20shadow.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20residents%20have%20witnessed%20the%20Sangti%20river%2C%20once%20flowing%20crystal%20clear%2C%20burdened%20by%20the%20unwelcome%20weight%20of%20plastic%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20like%20the%20beautiful%20black-necked%20crane%20soaring%20above%20the%20majestic%20Himalayan%20hills%2C%20the%20residents%20of%20Sangti%20valley%20have%20taken%20flight%20against%20the%20encroaching%20tide%20of%20pollution.%20If%20you%20visit%20the%20area%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20yourself%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20a%20village%20transitioning%20into%20a%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Ittisha%20Sarah%2C%2032%2C%20stumbled%20upon%20this%20hidden%20gem.%20Her%20visit%20as%20a%20tour%20instructor%20for%20a%20group%20of%20school%20kids%20travelling%20from%20Assam%20%E2%80%94%20after%20completing%20her%20Social%20Design%20course%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Ambedkar%20University%20%E2%80%94%20became%20a%20reverie%20she%20would%20catch%20on%20to%20two%20years%20later.%20This%20would%20lead%20to%20the%20Sangti%20Project%20%E2%80%94%20an%20attempt%20to%20balance%20development%20with%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbimonthly-waste-segregation_11zon-1730809756-500x667.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sangti%20residents%20actively%20participate%20in%20waste%20segregation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbimonthly-waste-segregation_11zon-1730809756-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbimonthly-waste-segregation_11zon-1730809756-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbimonthly-waste-segregation_11zon-1730809756-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbimonthly-waste-segregation_11zon-1730809756-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbimonthly-waste-segregation_11zon-1730809756-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbimonthly-waste-segregation_11zon-1730809756-150x200.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbimonthly-waste-segregation_11zon-1730809756.jpg%201393w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-374402%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESangti%20residents%20actively%20participate%20in%20waste%20segregation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Sangti%2C%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20West%20Kameng%20district%2C%20dedicate%20three%20days%20a%20month%2C%20based%20on%20the%20Buddhist%20lunar%20calendar%2C%20to%20ensure%20all%20waste%20in%20the%20village%20is%20managed%20efficiently.%20Ittisha%20and%20her%20organisation%20%E2%80%98Northeast%20Waste%20Collective%E2%80%99%20have%20received%20recognition%20from%20the%20district%20administration%20and%20the%20State%20Government%20for%20establishing%20the%20community-based%20management%20model%20aimed%20at%20making%20Sangti%20a%20zero-waste%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(Northeast%20Waste%20Collective)%20have%20been%20doing%20good%20work%3B%20and%20the%20bes