get%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompostable%20and%20biodegradable%20tableware%20%3C%2Fa%3Emade%20from%20sugarcane%20residue%20(bagasse).%20Brands%20like%20Haldiram%E2%80%99s%2C%20Rebel%20Foods%2C%20and%20Caf%C3%A9%20Coffee%20Day%20are%20their%20customers%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20sugarcane%20pulp%20to%20make%20moulded%20fibre.%20We%20also%20worked%20towards%20flexible%20packaging%20using%20natural%20products%20for%20items%20like%20potato%20chip%20bags%2C%20chocolate%20wrappers%2C%20cookies%2C%20and%20biscuits.%20This%20was%20quite%20challenging%20as%20these%20products%20need%20longer%20shelf%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20investing%20in%20R%26amp%3BD%2C%20the%20company%20achieved%20scalability%2C%20a%20critical%20factor%20that%20helped%20it%20stabilise%20and%20emerge%20from%20uncertainty.%20This%20focus%2C%20along%20with%20Ved%20finding%20his%20purpose%2C%20led%20to%20a%20turnover%20increase%20to%20Rs%20200%20crore%20in%20FY%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20company%20rebranded%20from%20Yash%20Papers%20to%20Pakka%20Limited%2C%20meaning%20%E2%80%98packaging%20with%20a%20soul%E2%80%99.%20Ved%20stepped%20down%20as%20CEO%20and%20MD%2C%20transitioning%20to%20a%20strategy%20lead%20role%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20he%20truly%20valued.%20In%20this%20new%20position%2C%20he%20prioritised%20strategic%20initiatives%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20new%20business%20opportunities%2C%20while%20delegating%20day-to-day%20operations%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20moved%20from%20being%20a%20pulp%20and%20paper%20company%20to%20being%20a%20sustainable%20packaging%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ved.%20The%20company%20diversified%20its%20offerings%20into%20three%20main%20categories%3A%20paper%2C%20moulded%20products%2C%20and%20flexible%20packaging.%20All%20products%20are%20primarily%20made%20from%20sugarcane%20bagasse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20sustainable%20future%3A%20Commitment%20to%20green%20operations%20and%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20creating%20sustainable%20packaging%2C%20the%20company%20is%20committed%20to%20operating%20sustainably%20%E2%80%94%20a%20legacy%20started%20by%20K%20K%20Jhunjhunwala%20in%201995%2C%20when%20he%20established%20a%20power%20plant%20powered%20by%20rice%20husks%2C%20enabling%20the%20company%20to%20generate%20its%20own%20energy%20and%20go%20off-grid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVed%20has%20continued%20this%20legacy%2C%20now%20producing%20electricity%20with%20an%208.5%20MW%20plant%20that%20operates%20entirely%20on%20biomass-based%20energy.%20He%20shares%20that%20both%20raw%20materials%20and%20fuel%20are%20sourced%20locally%2C%20within%20200%20km%20of%20their%20factory%20in%20Ayodhya.%20While%20focusing%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354235%2Fsaurabh-mehta-delhi-makes-biodegradable-pen-bamboo-coconut-oil-sustainable-stationery-no-plastic%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20inputs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ved%20also%20aimed%20to%20minimise%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20effluent%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fpakka2-1730299637.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pakka%20generates%20its%20own%20electricity%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fpakka2-1730299637.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fpakka2-1730299637-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fpakka2-1730299637